description: [``botocore``] AWS Mainframe Modernization Application Testing is an AWS Mainframe Modernization service feature that automates functional equivalence testing for mainframe application modernization and migration to AWS, and regression testing.
[``botocore``] The backupstorage client has been removed following the deprecation of the service.
[``botocore``] Tagging support for Traffic Mirroring FilterRule resource
[``botocore``] SDK changes for self-managed vpc endpoint to OpenSearch ingestion pipelines.
[``botocore``] Updates to remove DC1 and DS2 node types.
[``botocore``] Introducing RotationToken parameter for PutSecretValue API
[``botocore``] This release updates request validation regex to account for non-commercial aws partitions.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for Amazon EventBridge as an email sending events destination.
